com.revature.caliber.services

Class ReportingService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revature.caliber.services.ReportingService

  • @Service
public class ReportingService
extends java.lang.Object
    Exclusively used to generate data for charts Provides logic concerning grade and aggregated data sets. Application logic has no business being in a DAO nor in a Controller. This is the ideal place for calculations Team !Uncharted
    Author:
    Pier Yos, Hossain Yahya, Yanilda Peralta, Igor Gluskin, Ateeb Khawaja
